asset.name: PrimeNumber #26849
asset.description: Prime Numbers is a DAO that generate scholarships for students and our community through NFTs and DEFI. However, it is much more than that. Ecosystems based on NFTs are coming online at an astonishing rate, but Prime Numbers is uniquely incorporating a staking inside NFTs and a game with their NFTs in 2022. Prime Numbers is the first DAO, the first NFT project and the first game on XDC Network.

Ecosystems based on NFTs are coming online at an astonishing rate, but Prime Numbers is uniquely incorporating a staking inside NFTs and a game with their NFTs in 2022. Prime Numbers is the first DAO, the first NFT project and the first game on XDC Network.

Ecosystems based on NFTs are coming online at an astonishing rate, but Prime Numbers is uniquely incorporating a staking inside NFTs and a game with their NFTs in 2022. Prime Numbers is the first DAO, the first NFT project and the first game on XDC Network.
